    dc:description "Figure 2. (a) Amynthas retortus Sun and Jiang sp. nov., holotype, spermathecal pore region; (b) A. retortus sp. nov., male pore region; (c) A. retortus sp. nov., intestinal caecum; (d) A. retortus sp. nov., spermathecae. (e) Amynthas orbicularis Sun and Jiang sp. nov., holotype, dorsal view of spermathecal pores; (f) A. orbicularis sp. nov., male pore region; (g) A. orbicularis sp. nov., intestinal caecum; (h) A. orbicularis sp. nov., prostate gland region; (i) A. orbicularis sp. nov., spermathecae." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3994515/files/figure.png" ;
